    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Subject: UNKNOWN OBJECT OVER OAK RIDGE, TENNESSEE, MARCH 1, 1950",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "VITAL FACILITIES",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "INTERNAL SECURITY - [unclear]",
      "status": "needs_image_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "[REDACTED] is reported to have detected on his radar equipment an object directly",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "over Oak Ridge, Tennessee, at an altitude of 40,000 feet at 11:15 p.m.,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "March 1, 1950. On March 2, 1950, he advised that his radar equipment",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "recorded an object about 100,000 feet high and approximately 41 miles from",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "his home in Knoxville at 11:18 a.m. on that date. It was reported that the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Naval Reserve radar equipment at Knoxville, Tennessee, did not detect an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "object on any occasion but stated that the equipment was not considered",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "efficient for aircraft at extreme altitudes. It was further reported that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "that qualified persons at Oak Ridge, questioned [REDACTED] and examined his radar",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "equipment. They reportedly found his equipment not too reliable and felt that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "[REDACTED] was technically wrong on some of his radar theory. The reliability",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "of [REDACTED] was also questioned due to some degree of inebriation.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "The above confirms information telephonically furnished to [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "by this Bureau to [REDACTED] of your office. No investigation is being conducted",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "but in the event additional information comes to our",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
